result.formatted_address: 60-62號 S Wall Rd, Kowloon City, Hong Kong
result.name: Chong Fat Chiu Chow Restaurant

reviews.text: Super oily and unreasonably expensive. The prices are akin to fine dining restaurants but nowhere near the quality. Don’t go. Save your cash. And your tummy space. Go next door. Trust me on this.

A Chiu Chow restaurant with long history. The shop is very old fashioned without much decorations. The food is very genuine Chiu Chow style dishes. Recommended the goose slices and cold crabs. It's a little pricey compare to other restaurants of similar range though.

Traditional Chiu Chow restaurant, old style and no decoration.  Honestly the cool lobster and goose meat slides are only of average quality.  Portion is rather small and quite pricey.  However, sweet taro paste was quite good.  Service is okay but like most old style restaurants, staff are more attentive to regular customers than newcomers.

When you come here, you expected no service at all. The eq of the waiter is below 0. Standard “HK service” other place have better Chiu Chow food.
The seating plan is the worst, they try to push as much people in their restaurant as possible while they don’t care if it’s comfortable .

Old fashioned eateries that still lives in its golden glory. The quality of two most common Chiu Chow dishes - marinated duck and stir-fried flat noodles with beef fillet in satay sauce was disappointing.

result.adr_address: 香港九龍城城南道60-62號
result.name: 創發潮州飯店

reviews.text: 食物味道很好😍

九龍城老牌潮州打冷
魚飯 鳯尾魚 花生豬尾 打麵線  咸菜胡椒豬肚湯
價錢有平有貴！你要懂得點菜
苦瓜湯 新鮮鵝腸 水瓜烙
傳統潮州酒家， 屹立九龍城多年，價錢豐儉由人，僱客可在大堂攤檔選擇心水食物，包括傳统鹵水食品， 琳瑯滿目，即時泡製。
Super oily and unreasonably expensive. The prices are akin to fine dining restaurants but nowhere near the quality. Don’t go. Save your cash. And your tummy space. Go next door. Trust me on this.
